\ Hello World in MiniForth

." Hello, MiniForth!" CR

\ Stack manipulation demo
10 20 + .  CR
." 10 + 20 = 30" CR

\ Word definition
: SQUARE ( n -- n*n ) DUP * ;
: CUBE ( n -- n*n*n ) DUP SQUARE * ;

5 SQUARE . CR
3 CUBE . CR

\ Variable demo
VARIABLE counter
0 counter !
counter @ 1 + counter !
." Counter: " counter @ . CR
